{
  "id": "adv_main_03_05_01",
  "title": "BIG4編1章21話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。私を……\n月のテンペストから脱退させて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san. I…\nplease let me withdraw from Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7024889179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 9.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "な……っ\n……理由を聞かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh…at!\n…Tell me why.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんに負けてから、ずっと考えていたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been thinking about it ever since we lost to DoriKyun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "私達は……月ストは\n出来る限りのことをしてきたと思っています",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We… Moon Tempest\nhave done everything we could‚ I think.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.9333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "どうすれば成長出来るか\n話し合いだって何度もしてきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We talked many times about how to grow‚\nand we’ve always done our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、I-UNITYではスリクスに\n後少しのところで勝てなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But at I-UNITY‚ we lost to IIIX\nby a hair‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.166666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "今度こそ、と思った今回もまるで歯が立たなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and when we thought we could finally win‚ we were no match for them at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4333335877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "今までと同じ努力を続けても\nこれ以上先に進めないって気付いたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized that even if we keep putting in the same effort‚\nwe won’t be able to move forward anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3333335877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だからって……どうして月ストを\n脱退するって話になるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But why… why are you talking about withdrawing\nfrom Moon Tempest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1333335877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "月ストは、本当に素晴らしいグループです\nみんな優しくて、努力家で、チームワークもある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest is a truly wonderful group.\nEveryone is kind‚ hardworking‚ and we have great teamwork.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.4466067591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、それだけじゃ……\nもっともっと上へは行けないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that alone isn’t enough…\nit’s not enough to go higher.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんと戦って、そのことを痛感しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized that keenly when we fought DoriKyun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "ああいう、相手を打ち負かすという強い心がなければ\nアイドルとして生き残っていくことは出来ないんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Without that kind of strong will to defeat your opponent‚\nyou can’t survive as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "今の私に足りないのは……圧倒的な『個』の力です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I lack now… is overwhelming individual strength.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1666631063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "脱退した後はどうする\n月ストにはもう……戻らないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you going to do after you withdraw?\nAre you… not coming back to Moon Tempest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 88.633329773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "一時的な脱退……のつもりです\nでも、具体的にいつ戻るかは分かりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m thinking of it… as a temporary withdrawal.\nBut I don’t know when I’ll be back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "私自身が納得出来る状態まで成長しないと……\nこんな勝手なことをする意味がないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to grow to a point where I’m satisfied…\notherwise there’s no point in doing something so selfish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、きっとみんな怒るだろうから……戻ろうとしても\n受け入れてもらえるか分かりませんけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But everyone will probably be angry… so even if I try to come back‚\nI don’t know if they’ll accept me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃の意志は分かった\n俺も、敗北の大きさの意味は分かってるつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand your will‚ Kotono.\nI also understand the weight of this defeat.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.6333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、俺の方でも何か出来ないか探ってる\nだから……少し時間をくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m looking into what I can do on my end.\nSo… can you give me some time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.4000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 128.2833343506
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 128.5333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "本当に……これで良かったのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did I… really do the right thing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 134.5166737874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……少し時間をくれないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Can you give me some time?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.5666737874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 138.6833312988
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに……\n辛そうな顔、させちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nI made you worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.8333328248,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "……ううん、迷ってる時間なんてない\n私はもう、決めたんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ I don’t have time to hesitate.\nI’ve already made up my mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.2333267212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 154.3499918619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "（今は謝らない。私には……謝る資格なんてない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I won’t apologize now. I don’t… have the right to apologize.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3999918619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01/sud_vo_adv_main_03_05_01-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "（いつか必ず……もう一度、みんなの力になるんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Someday‚ I will definitely… become everyone’s strength again.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6333251952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1666585285,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1199.9969482999973,
          "startTime": 171.3666554768
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 171.2666676839
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 171.3666554768
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
